<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idcc34cc16-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s45101"><num value="45101">§ 45101.</num><heading> Definition</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In this chapter, “controlled substance” means any substance under section 102 of the Comprehensive Drug Abuse Prevention and Control Act of 1970 (<ref href="/us/usc/t21/s802">21 U.S.C. 802</ref>) specified by the Administrator of the Federal Aviation Administration.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idcc34cc17-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70">(<ref href="/us/pl/103/272/s1/e">Pub. L. 103–272, § 1(e)</ref>, <date date="1994-07-05">July 5, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/1221">108 Stat. 1221</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
